# Commercial layers must NOT be excluded — needed by the Dockerfile
# for cloud builds. ``just gcp build`` rsyncs the sibling repos into
# ``_extra_packages/`` here and removes it after the build completes;
# the Dockerfile's builder stage pulls from this directory via
# ``--build-context extra-packages=./_extra_packages`` when the
# hosted build is active.
!_extra_packages/
